class TResult(types.TypedDict):
    """Record the result of validation."""
    
    reason: NotRequired[str]
    valid: bool

class TModel(types.TypedDict):
    """Record validation result of a model."""

    properties: NotRequired[TProperties]
    result: TResult

class TSpec(types.TypedDict):
    """Record validation result for a specification."""

    models: NotRequired[TModels]
    result: TResult
